# Seed policy for {{.Module}}, loaded into casbin_rule on a fresh install.
# This file is yours — ix renders it once and never re-merges it.
#
# Format (matches the model's policy/role definitions):
#   p, <sub>, <dom>, <obj>, <act>, <cond>, <eft>
#   g, <user>, <role>, <dom>
#
# Example: an ADMIN role with cross-tenant access, and one admin user.
